nextSentence: Using state-of-the-art LLMs such as LLaMA-3-8B, GPT-4o, and Claude 3.5 Sonnet, PMP achieves state-of-the-art performance on GPT-4o on MUStARD and SemEval2018.
targetSentence: Sarcasm detection is a significant challenge in sentiment analysis due to the nuanced and context-dependent nature of verbiage. [SEP] We introduce Pragmatic Metacognitive Prompting (PMP) to improve the performance of Large Language Models (LLMs) in sarcasm detection, which leverages principles from pragmatics and reflection helping [MASK] interpret implied meanings, consider contextual cues, and reflect on discrepancies to identify sarcasm. [SEP] Using state-of-the-art LLMs such as LLaMA-3-8B, GPT-4o, and Claude 3.5 Sonnet, PMP achieves state-of-the-art performance on GPT-4o on MUStARD and SemEval2018.
